Chun-sim. (Sokongan Pentadbir Pantau di
kissasia.cam atau kisskh.org)

00:03:34.631 --> 00:03:35.882
Itulah awak!

00:03:46.727 --> 00:03:48.228
Apa yang kau buat dengan Chun-sim?

00:03:49.938 --> 00:03:51.064
Maaf?

00:03:52.107 --> 00:03:53.066
Apa yang anda…

00:03:53.984 --> 00:03:55.110
Lihat.

00:03:57.779 --> 00:03:59.239
Ia sangat jelas.

00:04:05.328 --> 00:04:08.623
Awak nampak seperti manusia sepenuhnya,
