01:00:21.815 --> 01:00:23.787
{\an8}Nampaknya,
dia memperoleh 500 juta won seminggu.

01:00:23.870 --> 01:00:25.831
{\an8}Saya sangat bangga kerana saya adalah diri saya.

01:00:25.914 --> 01:00:27.249
{\an8}Lama tak jumpa, Si-yeol.

01:00:27.332 --> 01:00:29.376
{\an8}- Adakah dia betul-betul tidak mengenali saya?

01:00:29.459 --> 01:00:30.669
{\an8}

